dashboardItems.text:
*HIV CBS CASCADE: NOTES*

All totals are cumulative and updated nightly. For each period and count, total excludes enrollments where latest status was "DEAD" or "TRANSFER OUT".

*PLHIV*: All enrollments in HIV CBS Tracker
*PLHIV on ART*: Patient enrolled on ART
*PLHIV eligible for viral load test*: Must have had positive HIV test results 6 months before the latest event.
*PLHIV who have viral load results*: Must have had positive HIV test results 6 months before the latest event, and had VL result reported.
*PLHIV who have viral load suppression*: Must have had positive HIV test results 6 months before the latest event, and had VL result reported, where VL < 1000.

Enrollments by Sex, Age Brackets, and Mode of Transmission. 
Enrollments are cumulative, excluding enrollments with status "DEAD" or "TRANSFER OUT". Location is site of enrollment, not latest service.
